<section xml:id="sec_force-and-potential-energy" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Force and Potential Energy</title>

      <video youtube="tIn6UMjLXTo"><description>Discussing the relationship between force and potential energy.</description></video>

<definition xml:id="def_force-pe">
	<title>Potential Energy Diagrams</title>
	<statement>
	<p>Potential energy and the corresponding conservative force are related (in one dimension, <m>x</m>) by <m>\vec{F} = -\frac{dU}{dx}\hat{x}</m>.</p>
	</statement>
	</definition>

